name: Excel LC Pipeline Status
query:
SELECT
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.file_no as "File No:Data/File No:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.brand as "Brand:Data/Brand:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.lot_no as "Lot No:Data/Lot No:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.supplier_name as "Supplier Name:Data/Supplier Name:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.actual_pi_no as "Actual PI No:Data/Actual PI No:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.actual_pi_value as "Actual PI Value:Currency/Actual PI Value:150",
	`tabExcel LC Pipeline`.lc_pi_no as "LC PI No:Data/LC PI No:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.lc_pi_value as "LC PI Value:Currency/LC PI Value:150",
	`tabExcel LC Pipeline`.lc_no as "LC No:Data/LC No:150",
	`tabExcel LC Pipeline`.lc_date as "LC Date:Date/LC Date:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.lc_opening_bank as "LC Opening Bank:Data/LC Opening Bank:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.shipper as "Shipper:Data/Shipper:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.cnee_name as "CNEE Name:Data/CNEE Name:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.insurance_provider as "Insurance Provider:Data/Insurance Provider:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.freight_forwarder as "Freight Forwarder Name:Data/Freight Forwarder Name:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.on_board_date as "On Board Date:Date/On Board Date:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.container_size as "Container Size:Data/Container Size:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.carton_qty as "Carton Qty:Float/Carton Qty:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.bl_no as "BL No:Data/BL No:150",
	`tabExcel LC Pipeline`.final_destination as "Final Destination:Currency/Final Destination:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.carrier as "Carrier:Carrier/ETD:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.eta as "ETA:Date/ETA:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.ci_value as "CI Value:Currency/CI Value:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.boe_no as "BOE No:Data/BOE No:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.boe_date as "BOE Date:Date/BOE Date:150",
	`tabExcel LC Pipeline`.transport_agency as "Transport Agency:Data/Transport Agency:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.cnf_agent as "CnF Agent:Data/CnF Agent:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.etr as "ETR:Date/ETR:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.shipment_status as "Shipment Status:Data/Shipment Status:150",
    `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.pipeline_status as "Pipeline Status:Select/Pipeline Status:150"

FROM
  `tabExcel LC Pipeline`

WHERE
  `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.docstatus=0 OR `tabExcel LC Pipeline`.docstatus=1
